<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>Sacred Harp Barcelona</title>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
		<link
			href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=EB+Garamond:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap"
			rel="stylesheet"
		/>
		<style>
			* {
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}

			html {
				font-size: 18px;
			}

			body {
				font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", Georgia, serif;
				line-height: 1.8;
				color: #e8e0d5;
				background: #243530;
				/* padding: 1rem 1rem; */
				max-width: 580px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				min-height: 100vh;
				letter-spacing: 0.01em;
			}

			header {
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
				text-align: center;
			}

			h1 {
				font-family: "EB Garamond", Georgia, serif;
				font-size: 2.6rem;
				font-weight: 500;
				line-height: 1.1;
				/* letter-spacing: 0.08em; */
				text-transform: uppercase;
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
				margin-top: 0.5rem;
				color: #f4b87a;
			}

			.subtitle {
				font-style: italic;
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				opacity: 0.7;
				letter-spacing: 0.08em;
			}

			section {
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
			}

			section:last-of-type {
				margin-bottom: 0;
			}

			h2 {
				font-size: 0.9rem; /* bumped up from 0.85rem */
				font-weight: 600;
				letter-spacing: 0.15em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: #f4b87a; /* warm amber accent */
			}

			p {
				font-size: 1.15rem;
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
				margin-top: 0rem;
			}

			p:last-child {
				margin-bottom: 0;
			}

			.details {
				font-size: 1.3rem;
				line-height: 2.2;
			}

			a {
				color: #f4ece3;
				text-decoration: none;
				border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(244, 236, 227, 0.25);
				transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
			}

			a:hover {
				border-color: rgba(244, 236, 227, 0.8);
			}

			.listen {
				text-align: center;
				padding: 0.5rem 0;
				border-top: 1px solid rgba(244, 236, 227, 0.1);
				border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(244, 236, 227, 0.1);
			}

			.listen a {
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.15em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				border-bottom: none;
				opacity: 0.7;
				transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
			}

			.listen a:hover {
				opacity: 1;
			}

			footer {
				text-align: center;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				opacity: 0.4;
				margin-top: 5rem;
			}

			#section-after-logo {
				margin-top: -1rem;
				position: relative;
				padding: 0 1rem;
			}

			.overflow-centered {
				display: block;
				position: relative;
				margin-top: -1.5rem;
				left: 50%;
				transform: translateX(-50%);
				width: 100%;
				max-width: none;
				height: auto;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<header>
			<h1>Sacred Harp Barcelona</h1>
		</header>

		<img
			src="../JUSTBIRDCAUSEYOUHATEMYTYPETASTE.png"
			class="overflow-centered"
		/>

		<section id="section-after-logo">
			<h2>What it is</h2>
			<p>Community folk-singing of traditional acapella music.</p>
			<ul>
				<li>No auditions, rehearsals or performances.</li>
				<li>No money or experience needed.</li>
				<li>Friendly, inclusive community open to all.</li>
			</ul>
			<p>We show up, we sing, we hang out. That's all.</p>

			<section>
				<h2>When &amp; Where</h2>
				<p>
					<a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/h1JWXzK7eTSFmJ9F9"
						>Thursdays, 7 - 9, MOB, Bail√®n</a
					>
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2>What it sounds like</h2>
				<iframe
					style="border: 0; width: 100%; height: 42px;"
					src="https://bandcamp.com/EmbeddedPlayer/album=2865413260/size=small/bgcol=333333/linkcol=ffffff/track=2370696986/transparent=true/"
					seamless
					><a
					href="https://corksacredharp.bandcamp.com/album/the-third-ireland-convention-2013-saturday"
					/></iframe
				>

				<section>
					<h2>What to bring</h2>
					<p>Nothing. We've got things to sing from, it's fine.</p>
				</section>

				<!-- <section>
				<h2>Get in touch</h2>
				<p>
					Questions? Email <a href="mailto:hello@example.com"
						>hello@example.com</a
					>
				</p>
			</section> -->
			</section>
		</section>
	</body>
</html>
